<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FP</title>
    <style>
        body, html, main {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .box {
            width: 866px;
            height: 589px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #d3d3d3;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin: 70px auto 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            top: 35px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .title2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            text-align: center;
            top: 90px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .line {
            width: 823px;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #000000;
            position: absolute;
            top: 99px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .button {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            width: 114px;
            height: 32px;
            background-color: #A0E9FF;
            position: absolute;
            top: 368px;
            left: 50%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .input {
            width: 290px;
            height: 20px;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;
            background-color: transparent;
            font-size: 16px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 233px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            padding-left: 7px;
        }

        .input:focus {
            outline: none;
        }

        .input2 {
            width: 290px;
            height: 20px;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;
            background-color: transparent;
            font-size: 16px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 331px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            padding-left: 7px;
        }

        .input2:focus {
            outline: none;
        }

        .back {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #ACACAC;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: absolute;
            text-decoration: none;
            top: 77px;
            left: 25px;
        }

        .make {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #ACACAC;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: absolute;
            text-decoration: none;
            top: 406px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .make2 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            top: 448px;
            left: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
            padding-left: 20px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .line2 {
            width: 823px;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #000000;
            position: absolute;
            top: 460px;
            left: 21px;
        }

        .button2 {
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 160px;
            height: 46px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            top: 489px;
            background-image: url('https://i.ibb.co/0GW2z8F/Kakao-Talk-20240826-155958604-06.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="background-color: #EFFFFD">
    <div class="box">
        <p class="title">로그인</p>
        <a href="/" class="back">< 돌아가기</a>
        <p class="title2">
            "성공은 자신을 발견하고"
            <br>
            "진로를 설계하는 과정에서 옵니다."
        </p>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <form action="/submitlogin" method="post">
            <input type="text" class="input" name="username" placeholder="사용자명">
            <input type="password" class="input2" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호">
            <button type="submit" class="button">로그인</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/signup" class="make" type="button">계정이 없으신가요?</a>
        <div class="make2">간편로그인</div>
        <div class="line2"></div>
        <div class="line3"></div>
        <button class="button2"></button>
    </div>
</body>

</html>